Package: epics-libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: EPICS libraries for clients and servers
 EPICS shared libraries.

Package: epics-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: epics-libs, epics-catools, epics-perl, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Suggests: epics-doc
Description: Files needed to develop new EPICS applications
 Libraries, headers, and utilities needed to develop applications
 targeted to the host system.

Package: epics-compat-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: epics-dev, epics-libs, epics-perl, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Suggests: epics-doc
Description: Files needed to develop new EPICS applications
 Libraries, headers, and utilities needed to develop applications
 targeted to the host system.
 This package contains additional files needed for compatibility with EPICS 3.13.x

Package: epics-catools
Architecture: any
Depends: epics-libs, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Command line utilities for EPICS
 EPICS utilities such as caget and caput.

Package: epics-perl
Architecture: any
Depends: epics-libs, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Perl bindings for for EPICS
 Perl bindings for for EPICS

Package: epics-doc
Architecture: all
Depends: epics-libs
Description: EPICS documentation
 Documentation for EPICS Base

Package: epics-rtems-mvme3100
Architecture: any
Depends: rtems-mvme3100, rtems-libbspext-mvme3100, epics-dev, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: EPICS targeted to the MVME3100
 EPICS for the MVME3100 powerpc based vme bus processor card

Package: epics-rtems-pc386
Architecture: any
Depends: rtems-pc386, epics-dev, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: EPICS targeted to the PC system with >= 386 cpus
 EPICS for the standard 386 compatible cpu and PC hardware.
